SLI (Slackel-Live installer) is a GUI to install or copy the live system (based on GTK+2).

Slackware-live is a dependency for SLI.

The SLKBUILD source package and binary 
can be found on http://www.slackel.gr/repo/source/slackel-source/slackware-live-installer-1.2.5/3/

